718
00:27:19,976 --> 00:27:22,016
Three, two, one.

719
00:27:23,496 --> 00:27:25,095
You're a nuisance.

720
00:27:25,095 --> 00:27:25,855
You can only see

721
00:27:25,855 --> 00:27:27,375
