804
00:30:30,535 --> 00:30:32,095
(It was because Dad and Mom
didn't pay enough attention to me.)

805
00:30:33,055 --> 00:30:34,815
(Because Deng Haiyang was a loser.)

806
00:30:37,335 --> 00:30:39,256
