847
00:35:29,496 --> 00:35:30,896
Okay, I'm surprised. It's lovely.

848
00:35:31,095 --> 00:35:32,016
So colorful.

849
00:35:32,255 --> 00:35:33,016
Listen.

850
00:35:33,376 --> 00:35:34,296
This isn't the main course.

851
00:35:34,575 --> 00:35:35,856
