856
00:35:42,856 --> 00:35:43,575
Hurry up and make a wish.

857
00:35:43,695 --> 00:35:44,336
Make a wish.

858
00:35:44,376 --> 00:35:45,296
A wish?

859
00:35:46,296 --> 00:35:47,575
